l - used to have to do the house linen and - that, see that that was all right and that but her clothes she used to - do herself if they wanted any mending or - used to get a dressmaker to do them you see. But we used to have to see that the }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14953070\charrsid14840390 bed linen}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390  and 
