No. No, not at those places, no, they used to - they did used to buy that, but - they used to - have the cellars you see and used to - buy all that, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2896308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 They all grew their own fruit and vegetables?
