\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2896308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 But you don't remember any kind of musical evenings apart from that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8743498 AG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 No. No, only just that, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2896308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 They didn't have sort of playing the piano and singing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8743498 AG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 
The - the - old Sir Fortescue used to have a - spinet - spinnet - he used to - oh we used to love to hear him
 play that, us girls used to listen at the door. - when he used to play that. Used to say, he's on - he's on the spinnet, come - you come and listen and we used to - listen like that at the door. And then she had one in her - boudoir too. They used to hav
e
 the bedroom - like was one wing, she - they'd have the bedroom, then there was his bathroom, and then this side was her boudoir, there used to be a piano in there. See? And he used to go in there sometimes and have a tune on it. Yes. He could do the spin
net - I used to love to hear that spinnet, more than the piano. It had got a different - tone somehow, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2896308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 Nobody sang songs while he was playing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8743498 AG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 No. No, didn't sing, no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2896308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 So you don't remember anywhere where they had these sort of evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8743498 AG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 
No. No. No. No. No. But I tell you he did used to play this spinnet, I used to love that. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2896308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 At Porters Hall, they didn't do anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8743498 AG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 
I'll tell you what they had there, what she used to play sometimes was the pi
ano, but she couldn't play the piano, and do you know they had rolls of paper - was in a quite - I don't know if I can explain to you quite - rolls of - and they used to put it on somehow and that would play - play this piano. I don't know how they fixed 
it now, I've really forgotten it. But they'd have these rolls and it was all the music on it, and there was holes in it - what - holes in it and it used to play the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14953070\charrsid14840390 piano}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 . How it was done \{ILLEGIBLE\} know. You might perhaps find out from \{BLANK\}
 they would know better than me but - but I remember that, these rolls - these rolls like - almost like a toilet roll it was, and how they fixed it and how it - how it -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2896308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 I think I've seen an organ which was done like that.
