\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2896308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 It's a kind of machine playing really isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8743498 AG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3175380\charrsid14840390 
Yes. Yes. Yes, it was interesting, yes. That's - that's what they had at Porters Hall 'cos she couldn't play the piano but they got one. - Mm.
